PoW vs PoS
PoW (Proof of Work)
1.	Verification done by miners
2.	Drawbacks:
o	High investment
o	Electricity consumption
o	Needs to run 24/7
3.	Miners receive block rewards
PoS (Proof of Stake)
1.	Validation done by validators (people who stake coins)
2.	Validators hold money as stake
3.	Block rewards are given automatically
4.	Even if system is off (through masternodes), rewards continue

